                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18011202-18-defend199 t18011202-18-punish87"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18011202-18-person213">
                  Ann 
                  Rockall
               <interp inst="t18011202-18-person213" type="surname" value="Rockall"></interp>
